name: Executioner Charles-Henri Sanson (Death ZoLLaR #DZ1)
description:
Each Death ZoLLaR alludes to a specific part of mortality from the past, present and future.
 
Part of the Z Mortality Monetary System, Death ZoLLaR #DZ1 abandons the idea of numerical currency by instead asking the ZoLLaR owner to apply a personal interpretation of how much we value different aspects of mortality. 

How much is death worth to you and yours? 

Created and issued by Zederal Reserve. 
Part of the Z Economy.
